{"tid":351311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最新一期的《EDGE》雜誌曝料Steam可能將在中國消失","createTime":"2017-08-08T02:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T10:42:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4b47ec35fa3e25235c215f6adab04ce56f3fbf","tid":351311,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:29:15.000Z","msg":"最近幾個月來，很多玩家都注意到Steam總是出現103、105無法連接等情況，這讓很多人開始擔心這是不是Steam即將被封禁的前奏。不論是在論壇、貼吧，還是微博、QQ群，關於Steam將從中國消失的傳言在坊間流傳甚廣，儘管更多時候這只是一種毫無根據的擔心，但對於已經習慣Steam提供的服務的玩家來說，本就處於灰色地帶的Steam未來究竟會如何，一舉一動總是牽動著他們的萬千心弦。而Steam客服之前在回應中國玩家「無法連接」這一疑問時也只是說這「跟地方服務器有關」「他們對此無能為力」。"},{"pid":"4abb1b17f73ca7f5bd40b4b04c290f7dca7e8320","tid":351311,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:30:29.000Z","msg":"bam9班掛狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0184806515d596bbc9c3a4dca8cafafbfd8176a2","tid":351311,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:30:40.000Z","msg":"在最新出爐的一期知名遊戲雜誌《EDGE》上，刊登了一篇名為《東諾》（Eastern Promise）的文章，似乎在某種側面上證實了這一傳言。這篇分析中國遊戲市場的文章開頭這樣寫道：一名騰訊內部高級經理在2016年11月《最終幻想15》中國發佈會後，向一名中國遊戲開發者透露了公司未來的一些計劃，其中一個重要信息就是：「等時機到了，Steam就會在中國不復存在」。考慮到作者Simon Parkin是為《紐約客》《衛報》寫作的知名記者，《EDGE》也是業內較有權威的老牌雜誌，這個傳聞似乎還是具有一定可信度的。<br />\n不過，考慮到文章開頭列出的案例發生於2016年11月，現在傳言是否有了變化，最新進展如何，我們不得而知。"},{"pid":"56b2f6bd2235242f2515852b79fc6ecefd3a3f1d","tid":351311,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:33:09.000Z","msg":"yeah <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10fcb9f6add0806680a463376e720981d61b73f8","tid":351311,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>yeah <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBam柒支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f6d375ea6df420e7a96bea0b4c199206e6fd7e","tid":351311,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5562fcbe1bcf727a0e6546ae91a60efa2317658a","tid":351311,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T03:13:14.000Z","msg":"有個壞處係少左中文翻譯(雖然殘體)<br />\n好處就多到數唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfdcbdda81ec5abac60063683a50beed29cd443","tid":351311,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T03:15:37.000Z","msg":"多謝黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又關住班網絡癲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3464fdead34fe5ae9ab3aec198a8eb5cb62704","tid":351311,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T03:15:38.000Z","msg":"正版野都無法在支那生存的"},{"pid":"a06444c4045d54f3816f27d7a0f8dc22f91202be","tid":351311,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T03:18:33.000Z","msg":"即刻少左班出cheat既支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2aed2c09e31993b32409b45beafdfc809862bd0","tid":351311,"uid":43285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:31:19.000Z","msg":"正呀 存檔死清光"},{"pid":"927db5a551c5fb72ea852f6437b80b2411d22af1","tid":351311,"uid":3326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:32:19.000Z","msg":"以後仲有冇得講 Taiwan no1撚狗？"},{"pid":"1b168266d512d3cfcf406c4b10246c22bde